        <Parent_String>tapestry Brussels (carpets) [300187319], Brussels carpets [300187157], pile-woven carpets [300187116], rugs by technique [300186946], rugs (textiles) [300185749], coverings and hangings by form [300185748], coverings and hangings by specific type [300185832], coverings and hangings [300205012], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
